{
  "title": "os",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<h1 cid=\"c5\" mdtype=\"heading\" class=\"md-end-block md-heading md-focus\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 2.25em; position: relative; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; cursor: text; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); width: inherit; font-family: 'Open Sans', 'Clear Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" class=\"md-expand\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">系统信号</span></h1><p cid=\"c7\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.8em 0px; width: inherit; position: relative; font-family: 'Open Sans', 'Clear Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c8\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> 系统信号是IPC中唯一种异步的通讯方式，信号被用来通知某个进程发生了什么，每个信号都以SIG前缀命名，在操作系统内部，这些信号都由整数代表。</span></span></p><blockquote cid=\"c9\" mdtype=\"blockquote\" style=\"margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Open Sans', 'Clear Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p cid=\"c10\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0px 0px 0.8em; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c11\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">*inux中可以用kill -l来查看系统支持的信号量,</span></span></p><p cid=\"c12\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.8em 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c13\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">在mac系统（unix）系统中只支持31个信号量</span></span></p><p cid=\"c14\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.8em 0px 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c15\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">在linux中支持64个信号量</span></span></p></blockquote><ul class=\"ul-list\" cid=\"c16\" mdtype=\"list\" data-mark=\"-\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.8em 0px; padding-left: 30px; font-family: 'Open Sans', 'Clear Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li cid=\"c17\" mdtype=\"list_item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; position: relative;\"><p cid=\"c18\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.5rem 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c19\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">编号为1-31号信号称为标准信号（不可靠信号），发送给系统的标准信号的处理顺序是不定的</span></span></p></li><li cid=\"c20\" mdtype=\"list_item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; position: relative;\"><p cid=\"c21\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.5rem 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c22\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">编号34-64号信号称为实时信号（可靠信号），发送给系统的实时信号的处理顺序是确定的（按发送先后）</span></span></p></li></ul><h4 cid=\"c23\" mdtype=\"heading\" class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"line-height: 1.4; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.25em; position: relative; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; cursor: text; width: inherit; font-family: 'Open Sans', 'Clear Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">信号的发送</span></h4><ul class=\"ul-list\" cid=\"c24\" mdtype=\"list\" data-mark=\"-\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.8em 0px; padding-left: 30px; font-family: 'Open Sans', 'Clear Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li cid=\"c25\" mdtype=\"list_item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; position: relative;\"><p cid=\"c26\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.5rem 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c27\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">键盘输入 ctrl-c</span></span></p></li><li cid=\"c28\" mdtype=\"list_item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; position: relative;\"><p cid=\"c29\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.5rem 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c30\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">硬件故障</span></span></p></li><li cid=\"c31\" mdtype=\"list_item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; position: relative;\"><p cid=\"c32\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.5rem 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c33\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">系统函数调用</span></span></p></li><li cid=\"c34\" mdtype=\"list_item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; position: relative;\"><p cid=\"c35\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.5rem 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c36\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">软件中的非法运算</span></span></p></li></ul><h4 cid=\"c37\" mdtype=\"heading\" class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"line-height: 1.4; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.25em; position: relative; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; cursor: text; width: inherit; font-family: 'Open Sans', 'Clear Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">响应信号方式</span></h4><ul class=\"ul-list\" cid=\"c38\" mdtype=\"list\" data-mark=\"-\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.8em 0px; padding-left: 30px; font-family: 'Open Sans', 'Clear Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li cid=\"c39\" mdtype=\"list_item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; position: relative;\"><p cid=\"c40\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.5rem 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c41\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">忽略</span></span></p></li><li cid=\"c42\" mdtype=\"list_item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; position: relative;\"><p cid=\"c43\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.5rem 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c44\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">捕获</span></span></p></li><li cid=\"c45\" mdtype=\"list_item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; position: relative;\"><p cid=\"c46\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.5rem 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c47\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">默认方式  linux中的信号都有其默认的处理方式</span></span></p></li></ul><h4 cid=\"c48\" mdtype=\"heading\" class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"line-height: 1.4; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.25em; position: relative; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; cursor: text; width: inherit; font-family: 'Open Sans', 'Clear Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">信号处理</span></h4><blockquote cid=\"c49\" mdtype=\"blockquote\" style=\"margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Open Sans', 'Clear Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p cid=\"c50\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c51\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">对于大多数信号都是可以自定义信号处理方式的，但是有部分信号是不能自定义信号处理方式的， 如SIGKILL和SIGSTOP</span></span></p></blockquote><h4 cid=\"c52\" mdtype=\"heading\" class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"line-height: 1.4; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1.25em; position: relative; margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; cursor: text; width: inherit; font-family: 'Open Sans', 'Clear Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">常用信号</span></h4><ul class=\"ul-list\" cid=\"c53\" mdtype=\"list\" data-mark=\"-\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.8em 0px 0px; padding-left: 30px; font-family: 'Open Sans', 'Clear Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li cid=\"c54\" mdtype=\"list_item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; position: relative;\"><p cid=\"c55\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.5rem 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c56\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">SIGINT 中断信号  ctrl - c</span></span></p></li><li cid=\"c57\" mdtype=\"list_item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; position: relative;\"><p cid=\"c58\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.5rem 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c59\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">SIGQUIT 推出信号 ctrl - \\</span></span></p></li><li cid=\"c60\" mdtype=\"list_item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; position: relative;\"><p cid=\"c61\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.5rem 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c62\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">SIGKILL 杀死信号（不能覆盖默认操作）</span></span></p></li><li cid=\"c63\" mdtype=\"list_item\" class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; position: relative;\"><p cid=\"c64\" mdtype=\"paragraph\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-margin-before: 1rem; -webkit-margin-after: 1rem; margin: 0.5rem 0px; width: inherit; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-line md-end-block\" cid=\"c65\" mdtype=\"line\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block;\"><span md-inline=\"plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">SIGSTOP 停止信号（不能覆盖默认操作）</span></span></p></li></ul>"
    }
  ]
